UWXg_jlYjITcpE_wZsg&oe=671E2960"}, {"file_name": "migrated_image.png", "id": "503266340619189", "uri": "https://scontent-iad3-1.oculuscdn.com/v/t64.5771-25/12727894_1244349155685243_631799352918016000_n.png?_nc_cat=104&ccb=1-7&_nc_sid=6e7a0a&_nc_ohc=Wku2WRiNolAQ7kNvgFMST-Q&_nc_zt=3&_nc_ht=scontent-iad3-1.oculuscdn.com&oh=00_AYDoKmp8gSc6n2_xaOQBOkVkSPQ9CX_Tkj_g0DE4kxkDag&oe=671E0AF0"}, {"file_name": "migrated_image.png", "id": "227997191679005", "uri": "https://scontent-iad3-1.oculuscdn.com/v/t64.5771-25/12533900_175818146265566_5173549375187582976_n.png?_nc_cat=109&ccb=1-7&_nc_sid=6e7a0a&_nc_ohc=PnoUkKkporAQ7kNvgH96dh8&_nc_zt=3&_nc_ht=scontent-iad3-1.oculuscdn.com&oh=00_AYBuj_mCnrXDTkOeRjmUlqmZ3J8o61bK3LmUAAuwRutsHQ&oe=671E3630"}], "video_trailer": null, "video_trailer_thumbnail": null, "display_name": "SwingStar Demo", "keywords": ["platformer", "puzzle", "rope", "swinging", "spiderman"], "long_description": "SwingStar is a wacky third-person physics puzzler set in a colorful universe. Your goal is to find and swing on a mysterious bell using a giant sticky hand attached to your head.\n\n- Touch Controller supported.\n- Explore all 30 colorful cartoon levels by swinging through enchanted deserts, bright forests, steep canyons, and many more bizarre and beautiful worlds.\n- Epic Boss Battle.\n- Unlock mysterious doors that unlock secret levels\n- Wacky power up items change the gameplay. Turbo Yo-yos swing you around, Air Cannons blast you high in the air, and The Grappling Jelly will suck you to it's gooey surface.\n- Brilliantly dreamy soundtrack.\n- Master each level to receive a perfect 3 Star rank.\n- Get all 84 stars to unlock the mysterious inter-dimensional zone.", "short_description": "SwingStar is a wacky third-person physics puzzler set in a colorful universe. Your goal is to find and swing on a mysterious bell using a giant sticky hand attached to your head.\n\n- Touch Controller supported.\n- In this demo Explore 30 colorful cartoon levels by swinging t